 \ln(y_n)=n\log\left(\frac{3n}{3n+1}\right). 
\lim_{x\to \infty}f(x)=0
\lim_{x \to \infty}g(x)=\infty
\lim_{x\to \infty}\left( 1+f(x) \right)^{g(x)}=e^{\lim_{x\to \infty}f(x)g(x)}
\lim_{n\to\infty} \left(\frac{3n}{3n + 1}\right)^n=\lim_{x\to\infty}\left(1-\frac{1}{3n+1}\right)^{n}=e^{\lim_{x\to \infty}\frac{-n}{3n+1}}=e^{\frac{-1}{3}}
